            <Col id="title18_0">Important Note(s) </Col>
            <Col id="title18_1">In case of lost verfication number, you can contact your home teacher to get the number resent to you (The verification number can be sent out a total of 10 times, including 1 time of resetting the number)</Col>
            <Col id="title18_2">Student personal data will not be saved &lt;fc v='#ff3f3f'&gt;Self-verification is not possible with verification number&lt;/fc&gt;</Col>
